{"title":"“湖畔”忠魂曲（七首）","authors":["汪静之"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“湖畔”忠魂曲（七首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪静之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应修人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤诚一片最忠贞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赴火蹈汤早许心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉骨碎身何足惜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坠楼促醒万民魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚是精神柔是石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党人魂硬石头柔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙华花染忠肝血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花耀丹心万古留。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潘漠华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝食斗争对敌怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懔然正气谁能侮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辣汤不怕灌千壶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂肯低头饮甘露！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯雪峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地雪山锻忠骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中营窟炼真金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠穆朗玛峰头雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至纯至洁是贞心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏金枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四凶魑魅践人权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱入蛇神牛鬼栏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躯体摧残虾背曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强赤胆未曾弯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢旦如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何处神州无血痕？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴森遍地是忠魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家中不惧惊雷隐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片忠诚护党心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中理想久氤氲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"净化灵魂似水晶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底无私至纯粹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充天塞地是忠心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注一：六位同志是我的同窗好友，知己至交，都是湖畔诗社社员。除谢旦如外，又都是共产党员。注二：“惊雷隐”指瞿秋白、杨之华夫妇白色恐怖时期在谢旦如家中隐姓改名住了两年。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}